# Credits-Only Billing

- The current product model is **recharge credits, deduct by usage, paid credits do not expire**.
- Do not add or restore subscription, recurring-plan, customer portal, cancel-subscription, or current-subscription behavior unless the user explicitly changes the product.
- Keep pricing page copy, account/billing UI, metadata, and JSON-LD aligned with the credits-only model. Remove stale monthly or subscription wording when touching affected files.
- Keep deduction semantics centralized. Recharge, usage accounting, and balance helpers should rely on shared credit helpers instead of duplicating balance math in routers.
- If a balance type expires or refreshes (for example invited credits or daily free credits), make that behavior explicit in both code and user-facing copy. Never imply paid credits expire if they do not.
